            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then chop your<strong> green beans</strong> into small pieces</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1644936113173-x200.jpg",
