      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped green beans</strong> and <strong>diced pepper</strong> to the<strong> </strong>pork mince and cook for 4-5 min further</p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1644936115292-x200.jpg",
